&lt;li&gt;Drive the development of backend infrastructure integrated with AI capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and support junior engineers through code reviews, technical guidance, and knowledge sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to Verkada&#39;s public API that customers use for integrations with their existing security and operations systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product managers, engineering leaders, and teams across the organization to define and deliver high-impact products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
