&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7219&quot; data-local-id=&quot;226a9b5cc791&quot;&gt;Participate in architecture and design discussions, offering thoughtful input and collaborating with senior engineers to identify tradeoffs and make well-informed decisions&lt;/p&gt;
