&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7502&quot; data-local-id=&quot;e7c919c39cac&quot;&gt;Take ownership of code in production, participate in on-call rotations, and help improve the reliability and maintainability of our systems over time.&lt;/p&gt;
