&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;4999&quot; data-local-id=&quot;8f3b380d7eb1&quot;&gt;LaunchDarkly is seeking a skilled Fullstack Engineer with experience utilizing Golang, React, and Typescript – bonus if you have experience with customer facing data-driven products!. You’ll collaborate closely with a cross-functional team of backend, frontend, and fullstack engineers, along with product managers, data scientists, and designers, to help build an experimentation platform that balances power and accessibility. In this role, you’ll contribute to the design, development, and maintenance of scalable, performant services using Go and RESTful APIs, and user experiences built with React and TypeScript. You’ll have opportunities to take ownership of projects, grow your technical expertise, and help improve the quality and reliability of our systems. We’re focused on building a best-in-class experimentation platform that enables customers to run impactful, data-driven experiments with ease and confidence, and we’re actively growing the team to deliver on this vision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;5989&quot; data-local-id=&quot;d15da491f2c8&quot;&gt;We are committed to delivering a leading experimentation platform that empowers our customers to run tests and data-driven experiments seamlessly and at scale. We have a robust product roadmap, and we are actively expanding our teams to execute on it.&lt;/p&gt;
