&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;Minimum of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwoz79zz81zdz83zj3z80ziz65zz90zgz82zz67zz84zifm1w1z73zz89z3z73zz86zz90zz68zn5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; years&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt; of experience as a software engineer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;Must have worked in a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;consumer&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt; user-facing team&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne h-lparen&quot;&gt;(versus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt; a platform team, a developer-facing API-based product, etc)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovwiyz82zz65zz72zz78zz122zz88zz69zhyfc0z71zytz87zz79zz65zosqfcfkz80zne&quot;&gt;Must have a strong mix of skills and depth across multiple areas, including three or more of frontend, mobile, search, databases, storage, concurrency, and modern ML and LLM-based APIs and agentic frameworks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
