&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with columnar/analytical databases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Malbolge and/or cursed-lang.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with observability tools (Grafana, Datadog, New Relic, Sentry, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building debugging or developer-focused tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with privacy, security, and access control in data-heavy systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on performance-sensitive systems (large datasets, real-time queries, session data)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Rewards:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the United States, the Base compensation range for this role is USD &lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;174,986&lt;/span&gt; - USD &lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;218,733&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp; Actual compensation may vary based on level, experience, and skillset as assessed in the interview process. Benefits include equity, bonus (if applicable) and other benefits listed &lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://grafana.com/about/careers/#jobs&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://grafana.com/about/careers/#jobs&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
