&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ Years experience developing software in a professional environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience building consumer-facing products at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient coding skills in modern languages and frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability with algorithms, data structures, data modeling, and schema design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or equivalent experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
